            <title>[PIG-3078] Make a UDF that, given a string, returns just the columns prefixed by that string</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/PIG-3078</link>
                <project id="12310730" key="PIG">Pig</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;This comes up fairly often, usually as the result of a join. Given that the resulting schema has the column name prepended, a udf in the following form could give just the columns from the desired relation:&lt;/p&gt;

